{
  "name": "ODBCErrors",
  "summary": "<p>每一个 <strong>ODBCError</strong> 对象都代表一个由最近的 ODBC 查询返回的错误。如果指定的 ODBC 查询运行时没有出现错误，则 <strong>ODBCErrors</strong> 集合为空。集合中错误的索引次序与 ODBC 数据源生成它们时的次序相同。您不能给该集合添加成员。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong>Application</strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Application/Application .htm#Application.ODBCErrors\">ODBCErrors</a></strong> 属性可返回 <strong>ODBCErrors</strong> 集合。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例刷新查询表一，并显示产生的所有 ODBC 错误。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> table = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">QueryTables</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    table.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Refresh</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> errs = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ODBCErrors</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (errs.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span> &gt; <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> range = table.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Destination</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n        range.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;The following errors occurred:&quot;</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= errs.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n            range.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Offset</span>(i, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = errs.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ErrorString</span>\n            range.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Offset</span>(i, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = errs.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SqlState</span>\n        }\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Query complete: all records returned.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一个 ODBC 错误的 SQL 状态错误。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> error = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ODBCErrors</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(error.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SqlState</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p><strong>ODBCError</strong> 对象的集合。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 <strong>Application</strong>对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>){\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>){\n            <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">MsgBox</span> (<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n        }\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span>{\n            <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">MsgBox</span> (<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n        }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Count",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Long</strong> 值，它代表集合中对象的数量。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 ODBC 错误的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ODBCErrors</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Item",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>从集合中返回一个对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示一个 ODBC 错误。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> error = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ODBCErrors</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`The following error occurred: <span class=\"hljs-subst\">${error.ErrorString}</span> : <span class=\"hljs-subst\">${error.SqlState}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一个 ODBC 错误赋值给G1单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> error = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ODBCErrors</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;G1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = error.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ErrorString</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Index",
          "type": "number（int4 精度）",
          "description": "<p>对象的索引号。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        }
      ],
      "returns": "<p>包含在集合中的一个 ODBCError 对象。</p>\n"
    }
  ]
}